dct_title_s: A map shewing ye situation of paradice and ye country inhabited by ye patriarchs
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "English Miles".
Shows topography, drainage, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of biblical events from Genesis throughout the map.
Features a decorative title cartouche with illustrations of a flora and fauna.
